Class SecurityAdminResources

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.ge.dspmicro.security.admin.api.SecurityAdminResources

  • public class SecurityAdminResources
extends Object
    Give easy access to a resource bundle strings. This class is designed as a singleton to provide basic localization with helper methods.
